hilarious 75 minute walk in the pumps of Boston's TOP female comedians. ALL New Line up!!

The High Heels Comedy Tour hosted by Jodi Sloane has competed in several comedy festivals including the Boston Comedy Festival and was a finalist in the Funniest Comic in New Hampshire Contest. The show also features Deb Farrar-Parkman who recently appeared in Girls Night Out in West Hartford CT's Playhouse in the Park and last year at the New York Underground Comedy Festival. Deb has also been featured in the Boston Comedy Festival's "Best of Boston Comics." Comedian and mom Jane Condon will also take the stage. Jane won "Audience Favorite" on NBC's Last Comic Standing and has also appeared on The Today Show and The View.

The comedy tour brings a lineup of three female comics and celebrates the unique styles of women in comedy. The tour is refined yet quirky. The women all bring something different to the stage, proving that not only can females be funny; they can deviate from predictable penis punch lines.
item.name: High Heels Comedy Tour- ALL New Line Up!
